            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">A poorly handled redundancy can lead to costly Industrial Tribunal cases. Our <strong>Strategic HR Consultants</strong> guide your management team through genuine role abolishment procedures, ensuring every step is documented, justified, and fully compliant. We also track re-engagement obligations so you never inadvertently breach the one-year rule when your business starts hiring again.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 style="font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--primary-navy);">Managing Collective Redundancies</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">If a redundancy affects a large number of employees within a short timeframe, it qualifies as a <strong>collective redundancy</strong>, triggering strict statutory consultation and notification procedures with employee representatives and the DIER.</p>

